column5: Anyone know what places in Dryden, ON that sell fishing licenses?

Probably many of the Gas Stations / bait shops along Rt. 17. If coming into town from Fort Francis as you pass the mill then cross the river there is a stop light. There is a gas station on the corner that used to sell bait and they also sold licenses a few years ago. Search Dryden, ON and there should be several places listed. Pooch
Licences are availible as soon as you cross the bridge by the paper mill at Fas Gas as well on highway 17 next to 7 eleven at K&A's bait & tackle.Fish ON
